main event: A witness observed a UFO object in the sky while sitting in the front yard.
interesting points: The witness was sitting in the front yard watching the sky to the northeast when they noticed the object.
The witness was not moving in a vehicle at the time of the sighting.
The witness was looking to the northeast when they first saw the object and looked to the northwest when they last saw it.
The witness was unable to provide an estimate of the object's position in degrees from true north or elevation from the horizon.
The report does not mention any photographs being taken of the object.
witnesses: one witness, sitting in the front yard
